154
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:21,840
They're your most precious stuff.

155
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,240
They should stay with Jiaxin forever.

156
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:27,320
Trust me.

157
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:30,400
