196
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:01,000
Okay.

197
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,400
See you.

198
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,640
Okay. Take care.

199
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,160
Bye.

200
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,280
Well.

201
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:07,960
Get aboard.

202
