Rest more.
You don't need to call me that often.

217
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:39,840
Got it, mom.

218
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,920
Take good care of yourself.

219
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:46,600
Take care.

220
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,120
