237
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,080
Yesterday.

238
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,600
Alright. No more talks.

239
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,800
Go clean up the room.

240
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:28,760
